{
  "timestamp": "2026-05-01T17:55:52.570Z",
  "level": "INFO",
  "type": "DB_QUERY",
  "collection": "blogs",
  "method": "insertOne",
  "query": {
    "title": "How I Resolved My Domain Suspension Issue with Hostinger and Radix",
    "slug": "domain-suspension-resulation",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "data": {
          "text": "What Caused the Suspension?",
          "level": 2
        },
        "_id": "69f4e928dc7e87b78f5487d7"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "When I checked my domain, I found it had been suspended due to a policy violation. After some digging on the registrar’s site and a few YouTube videos, I learned that Radix (the registry for .online domains) had flagged my domain for potential phishing activity."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e928dc7e87b78f5487d8"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "The real culprit? One of my old practice projects — an Amazon clone hosted at"
        },
        "_id": "69f4e928dc7e87b78f5487d9"
      },
      {
        "type": "quote",
        "data": {
          "text": "http://amazonclone.omkarcodes.online/."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e928dc7e87b78f5487da"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "I built this project six months ago simply to showcase my MERN stack skills. It was never meant for any malicious use, but because it closely mimicked Amazon’s interface, it triggered a phishing complaint (likely from a trademark owner), leading to the suspension of my entire domain."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e928dc7e87b78f5487db"
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "data": {
          "text": "How I Fixed It",
          "level": 2
        },
        "_id": "69f4e928dc7e87b78f5487dc"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "I immediately contacted Hostinger support via live chat. The support agent explained that since the suspension was applied by Radix (a higher authority), they couldn’t remove it directly. However, they guided me through the correct process:"
        },
        "_id": "69f4e928dc7e87b78f5487dd"
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "data": {
          "items": [
            "Visit the Radix unsuspension tool: https://radix.website/request-unsuspension",
            "Remove or take down any content that could be seen as abusive (in my case",
            "I temporarily disabled the Amazon clone sub-domain).",
            "Fill out the appeal form with a clear explanation."
          ],
          "ordered": false
        },
        "_id": "69f4e928dc7e87b78f5487de"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "I submitted the form explaining that the project was purely for educational and portfolio purposes, with no intention of phishing or misleading users."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e928dc7e87b78f5487df"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "To my surprise, Radix replied within 30 minutes and unsuspended my domain."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e928dc7e87b78f5487e0"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "Even after Radix lifted the suspension, the status wasn’t immediately updated in my Hostinger dashboard. I went back to Hostinger support, explained the situation, and they manually refreshed the status. Within a short time, my domain was fully active again."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e928dc7e87b78f5487e1"
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "data": {
          "text": "Steps to Unsuspend a Domain (If It Happens to You)",
          "level": 2
        },
        "_id": "69f4e928dc7e87b78f5487e2"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "Here’s a clear checklist you can follow:"
        },
        "_id": "69f4e928dc7e87b78f5487e3"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "Identify the Reason — Check why your domain was suspended (phishing, malware, policy violation, etc.).,\nContact Your Hosting Provider — Reach out to Hostinger (or your registrar) support first. They can guide you on the next steps.,\nRemove Problematic Content — Take down or modify any page/subdomain that might have triggered the flag.,\nSubmit an Appeal to the Registry — For .online domains, use Radix’s unsuspension form and clearly explain your case with proper context.,\nFollow Up — Keep communicating with both the registry and your hosting support until the status is updated on your dashboard.,\nPrevent Future Issues — Avoid hosting projects that heavily mimic big brands. Add clear disclaimers (e.g., “This is a demo/portfolio project”) if needed, and regularly monitor your domain health."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e928dc7e87b78f5487e4"
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "data": {
          "text": "Final Thoughts",
          "level": 2
        },
        "_id": "69f4e928dc7e87b78f5487e5"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "Domain suspensions can feel scary at first, especially when they happen without warning. But in most cases, they can be resolved quickly if you act fast and communicate clearly."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e928dc7e87b78f5487e6"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "This incident taught me the importance of being careful with clone projects and understanding how registries like Radix handle abuse reports."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e928dc7e87b78f5487e7"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "If you’re currently facing a similar issue with Hostinger or a Radix-managed domain, don’t panic — follow the steps above and reach out to support."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e928dc7e87b78f5487e8"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "Have you ever faced a domain suspension? Feel free to share your experience in the comments."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e928dc7e87b78f5487e9"
      }
    ],
    "excerpt": "A few months ago, I suddenly faced a domain suspension on my personal website omkarcodes.online. It was an unexpected headache, but after some investigation and quick action, I managed to get it resolved within a few hours.\n\nIn this post, I’m sharing exactly what happened and the step-by-step process that helped me unsuspend the domain.",
    "author": "69f4d0621048fe75c7bb4a22",
    "featuredImage": "",
    "tags": [
      "Hostinger",
      "Domain Name",
      "Readix"
    ],
